6040_translations":{"at":1772689426539,"data":{"id":3216040,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Santa Pongsapak Udomphoch is an actor member of the actor-based project group JASP.ER under GMMTV and Riser Music. He first entered the entertainment industry when he competed in GMMTV's star search competition \"Thailand School Star 2019.\"\n\nPreviously an artist under Studio Wabi Sabi, his contract with the company ended in April 2024 and he immediately signed with GMMTV. On December 19, 2024, he made his debut with Project JASP.ER with the release of their debut single \"Sadistic\".","name":"Pongsapak Udomphoch","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"พงศภัค อุดมโภชน์","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"彭萨帕克·安多姆珀驰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"彭薩帕克·安多姆珀馳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ポンサパック・ウドムポート","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Pongsapak Udomphoch, artisticamente conhecido como Santa, é um ator e dançarino tailandês sob o selo da GMMTV. Ele ganhou destaque inicial no Studio Wabi Sabi, onde protagonizou séries aclamadas como \"My Only 12%\" (2022), interpretando o personagem Cake, papel que demonstrou sua grande capacidade dramática e carisma.\n\nEm 2024, Santa assinou com a GMMTV, onde sua carreira atingiu um novo patamar de visibilidade ao protagonizar o arco principal de \"Perfect 10 Liners\" ao lado de Perth Tanapon. Esta série consolidou o \"casal\" PerthSanta, tornando-os um dos casais oficiais da agência. Reconhecido por seu talento excepcional na dança e performance, Santa também é membro do grupo JASP.ER (Riser Music). Sua trajetória é marcada pela versatilidade, transitando com facilidade entre o romance juvenil e performances musicais de alta energia.","name":"Santa Pongsapak Udomphoch","primary":false}}]}},"tv_44126_credits":{"at":1772689429242,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":87890,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Nam Sang-mi","original_name":"남상미","popularity":0.4048,"profile_path":"/yath31Jq5ajboNbMS200xFPirn1.jpg","character":"Lee Jung-Hye","credit_id":"525966c0760ee346619bdbbd","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1243254,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ahn Jae-wook","original_name":"안재욱","popularity":0.4627,"profile_path":"/dRFl6hb3LVTNtGFCvizaKoNhjKe.jpg","character":"Kang Ki-Tae","credit_id":"525966c0760ee346619bdbcd","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1352803,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Lee Pil-mo","original_name":"이필모","popularity":0.7377,"profile_path":"/sVnDH47xdLtTs3dyHkZu6LzWkGn.jpg","character":"Cha Soo-Hyuk","credit_id":"53eb8d090e0a26738900013f","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1354108,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Son Dam-bi","original_name":"손담비","popularity":0.5693,"profile_path":"/i0R2y8uIVGgLr0KZLDh8O2hzA7s.jpg","character":"Yoo Chae-Young","credit_id":"64ee8d4f27167100e35dd55e","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":577389,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Shin Da-eun","original_name":"신다은","popularity":0.4023,"profile_path":"/qJ47mJpGrLb4ge82xEMiFXedSzE.jpg","character":"Kang Myung-hee","credit_id":"5577e5e09251413c16001260","order":4},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1183807,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kim Min-gyu","original_name":"Kim Min-gyu","popularity":0.5171,"profile_path":"/wwH2lpOWbO1XCIFVV0Qef4OHUpY.jpg","character":"Ban Jin-Woo","credit_id":"56b093279251410b43001fa8","order":5},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":123019,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kim Gyu-ri","orig